	(281,NULL,NULL,2,'Za Za Bazaar','za-za-bazaar','Open All Year','<p><span style=\"font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">This brand new eatery in Bristol is the biggest restaurant in the UK - and is perfect for anyone who loves the buzz of a night market, has a sense of adventure and an appetite for fun.</span></p>','<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\">Za Za Bazaar serves food from all around the world, all produced by authentic chefs - you choose your country, pick your ingredients and stand back and watch as the Za Za chefs create dishes from around the world right before your eyes, using only the highest quality fresh ingredients.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\">From Tex-Mex to Indian, Za Za Bazaar has a choice of food that guarantees to keep the whole family happy. Try something new at the Far East stand which offers the best in Vietnamese, Thai, Chinese and Malayan cuisine; or stick to a familiar favourite such as Italian pasta, pizza and traditional British dishes from the European food island.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\">Kids will love the chance to browse the food and find what they fancy - and for big groups of friends it\'s an ideal night out. And once you\'ve sampled the delights from around the world, everyone will love the incredible desserts section.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\'