	(288,NULL,NULL,2,'Bordeaux Quay','bordeaux-quay','Open All Year','<p><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">Bordeaux Quay on Bristol&rsquo;s Harbourside is a restaurant, brasserie, bar, deli, bakery and cookery school, all under one roof. Housed in an elegant, converted warehouse on the waterfront, Bordeaux Quay offers the very best in seasonal, regionally sourced food and drink.</strong></p>','<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">the</em>&nbsp;Restaurant</strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />The Restaurant is situated on the first floor with stunning views of the harbour. It is both spacious and elegant and offers intimate meals for two to large scale events.&nbsp; The food is sophisticated, but firmly rooted in the traditions of European Provincial cooking. The extensive wine list includes many wines available by the glass and carafe. The wine bar is open to the public and is also perfect for a pre or post dinner drink and also offers a range of delicious classic and contemporary cocktails.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />Private dining facilities, wine tastings and event catering are also part of the restaurant experience.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">the</em>&nbsp;Brasserie</strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />The Brasserie is located on the ground floor of Bordeaux Quay in a large light-filled space that opens out onto an outside dining area on the water\'s edge. It has a relaxed, casual atmosphere serving first-class &ldquo;New York brasserie&rdquo; style food throughout the day. It opens on weekday mornings from 8am and weekend from 9am with a breakfast menu running until 11.30am. Lunch start at 12noon and the kitchen stays open through the day until 10.30pm. Coffee, pastries &amp; cakes are served all day. There is a great drinks list with a cozy bar area, special offers on drinks at certain times and a warm welcome to families.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">the</em>&nbsp;Cookery School</strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />The Cookery School offers fun, inspiring experiences in a relaxed, sociable &amp; attractive environment. The aim is to give students the knowledge and confidence to buy local, seasonal and fresh produce wherever possible through a team of chef-tutors who love to share their knowledge of how to cook delicious simple dishes that can be easily reproduced in the home environment.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Award-winning</strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />Bordeaux Quay was the UK&rsquo;s first restaurant to achieve a&nbsp;<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">gold rating&nbsp;</strong>under the Soil Association\'s sustainable catering scheme. The Food For Life Catering Mark, developed by the Soil Association and backed by Prince Charles, is the first to guarantee customers get a sustainable meal, with standards governing things such as food additives, animal welfare and the seasonality of the produce chefs use.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />In November 2011, the restaurant became the first Bristol restaurant to receive the highest possible national award for its all round sustainability, when it was one of only 19 restaurants in the UK to be recognised as a&nbsp;<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Three Star Sustainability Champion&nbsp;</strong>by the Sustainable Restaurant Association (SRA).<a class=\"hide_desktop\" href=\"b247://category/30/articles?subChannel=65\" rel=\"nofollow\">Here</a><a class=\"hide_tablet hide_mobile\" href=\"http://www.bristol247.com/category/asian\">Here</a></p>','BS4 3EN','51.45149512458951','-2.525454555761712',NULL,NULL,1,0,1,0,NULL,NULL,'2014-07-25 00:00:01','2014-07-25 09:27:21','2014-07-25 09:33:16',0),
	(289,NULL,NULL,2,'Brasserie Blanc','brasserie-blanc','TV celebrity chef Raymond Blanc','<p><span style=\"font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">Brasserie Blanc aims to provide the sort of menu and atmosphere where you can share a good meal with family and friends. For the TV celebrity chef Raymond Blanc, this is one of the greatest pleasures in life.&nbsp;</span></p>','<p><span style=\"font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">Serving modern and authentic French cuisine, each of Brasserie Blanc&rsquo;s dishes are handcrafted using only the finest ingredients, including sustainable, free-range, or freedom foods, as well as natural or wild produce. Now open every day for breakfast from 9am un<a class=\"hide_desktop\" href=\"b247://category/30/articles?subChannel=65\" rel=\"nofollow\">Here</a><a class=\"hide_tablet hide_mobile\" href=\"http://www.bristol247.com/category/asian\">Here</a>til 11am. Bon app&eacute;tit!</span></p>','BS4 3EN','51.42993448996811','-2.530947719824212',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,'2014-07-25 00:00:01','2014-07-25 09:33:33','2014-07-25 09:38:24',0),
	(290,NULL,NULL,2,'No.4 Clifton Village','no4-clifton-village','Georgian mansion house','<p><span style=\"font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">No.4 is a beautiful Georgian mansion house set in the heart of Clifton village. Independently owned and operated, the mansion boasts an award winning restaurant, private meeting spaces, intimate bar, secluded gardens and a 31 room hotel.</span></p>','<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\">At No.4 you will find huge sash windows stretching up to the ornate ceiling, solid oak floor boards and roaring open fires. At both the front and rear of the building are beautiful gardens. The gardens can be used for drinks parties, barbecues, afternoon tea, wedding parties or simply for a breath of fresh air.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />They take food seriously at No.4, whether you are looking for an intimate dinner or a private dining event, the food will be the talk of the party for years to come!</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\">Their a la Carte menu changes daily according to seasonal availability, cost and freshness of ingredients. All of their produce comes from in and around the Bristol and Somerset area, with the meats coming from Devon Rose Organic Farm and Ruby &amp; White, fish from Wing of St. Mawes and salads from Class 1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\">The wines at No.4 have been specially selected to accompany the flavours of the food, with a balance of Old World classics and a selection of younger, vibrant wines from around the world.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\">Opening hours:&nbsp;<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />Breakfast: Mon-Fri 7am - 9am and 8am - 10am at weekends&nbsp;<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />Lunch: on request&nbsp;<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />Dinner: 6pm - 10pm&nbsp;<a class=\"hide_desktop\" href=\"b247://category/30/articles?subChannel=65\" rel=\"nofollow\">Here</a><a class=\"hide_tablet hide_mobile\" href=\"http://www.bristol247.com/category/asian\">Here</a></p>','BS4 3EN','51.47865879418014','-2.5710306513427668',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,'2014-07-25 00:00:01','2014-07-25 09:38:28','2014-07-29 09:06:02',0),
	(291,NULL,NULL,2,'Hotel du Vin & Bistro','hotel-du-vin-bistro','Open All Year','<p><span style=\"font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">Hotel du Vin &amp; Bistro in central Bristol is open seven days a week for lunch and dinner, with the Bistro offering a menu rooted in classic European cuisine with a contemporary edge</span></p>','<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\">Praised in the national press time and time again, tables at the Hotel du Vin &amp; Bistro are highly sought after. The Bistro menu changes daily, featuring classic dishes supporting a philosophy of quality food cooked simply with the freshest of local ingredients, and all sensibly priced.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\">Private dining and wine-tasting experiences available.</p>','BS4 3EN','51.46764555436506','-2.5545511591552668',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,'2014-07-25 00:00:01','2014-07-25 09:42:25','2014-07-25 09:45:07',0),
	(292,NULL,NULL,2,'The Lido','the-lido','Open All Year','<p><span style=\"font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">At the Lido you are invited to take time out and just do nothing.</span></p>','<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\">The Lido is a cool, urban oasis tucked inside a courtyard of Georgian Terraces, nestled at the heart of historic Clifton, comprising of a spa, restaurant, outdoor heated pool, sauna, hot tub and steam room.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\">As befits this unique space, the spa prides itself on a special offering of tailor-made massages, using bespoke own-brand Lido oils. Whether you&rsquo;re looking for deep relaxation, mood enhancement, body rejuvenation or simply a blissful facial, the talented therapists will find the perfect treatment for you.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\">To complement the spa the award-winning restaurant will leave you wishing for more. Voted as runner up in &lsquo;Observer Food Monthly Awards&lsquo; for UK Best Restaurant, Head Chef, Freddy Bird, serves a menu to match the escapist spirit of the Lido. There&rsquo;s a taste of France, Spain and Morocco amongst others, prepared using the finest ingredients, many of which are sourced or foraged by Freddy locally.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\">The restaurant is situated on the old viewing gallery of the Clifton Pool and retains the original character features of the Victorian building with modern floor to ceiling windows, allowing spectacular views over the pool.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\">For full opening times of the spa, restaurant and pool please visit the website.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />www.lidobristol.com</p>','BS4 3EN','51.43614157194313','-2.588625942480462',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,'2014-07-25 00:00:01','2014-07-25 09:45:17','2014-07-25 09:51:22',0),
