	(296,NULL,NULL,2,'Las Iguanas - Harbourside','las-iguanas-harbourside','Open All Year','<p><span style=\"font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">Las Iguanas has been sharing its brand of Latin magic with restaurant goers since 1991, offering a tasty blend of the traditional and the new, with fresh ingredients, mouth-watering regional food and drink, and service from passionate people. Add intoxicating Latin rhythms and the rich colour palette of the southern hemisphere to the mix and you\'ll enjoy every minute and every mouthful.</span></p>','<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\">Las Iguanas works hard to bring fresh, tasty and authentic food to your table. The Latin recipes date right back to the 16th century, with a fusion of native Latin American Indian, Spanish, Portuguese and African influences. Las Iguanas signature dish, Xinxim Brasilian lime chicken, really is Pel&eacute;\'s favourite, and is the best example of this fusion, bringing together Latin, African and Portuguese flavours to create something really special.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\">In the bar, you&rsquo;ll find the perfect spot for a little pre- or post-dinner indulgence. Or if the mood takes you, just lounge with a cocktail or some tapas. Las Iguanas calls the bar the Cacha&ccedil;aria, because it\'s where they serve Las Iguanas Magnifica Cacha&ccedil;a. Cacha&ccedil;a is a spirit distilled from sugar cane and the national drink of Brasil. The restaurant and bar make its own near Rio de Janeiro and if you haven\'t tried it before, we know you\'ll enjoy it.<a class=\"hide_desktop\" href=\"b247://category/30/articles?subChannel=65\" rel=\"nofollow\">Here</a><a class=\"hide_tablet hide_mobile\" href=\"http://www.bristol247.com/category/asian\">Here</a></p>','BS4 3EN','51.45652269213197','-2.6158342707275324',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,'2014-07-25 00:00:01','2014-07-25 10:04:31','2014-07-25 10:06:39',0),
