	(337,NULL,NULL,2,'Steak Dinner With Wine For Two Â£21','steak-dinner-with-wine-for-two-21','at Farthings Country House Hotel (Up to 65% Off)','<p><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: OpenSansRegular, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;\">Couples or quartets can head to the Farthings Country House Hotel for a steak dinner. Each 6oz piece of meat will be served with hand-cut chips and a selection of seasonal vegetables. Diners will also be treated to a small glass of house wine. Customers should note that the menu is subject to change.</span></p>','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0185c6; text-decoration: none; font-family: OpenSansRegular, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;\" href=\"http://www.farthingshotel.co.uk/index.htm\">Farthings Country House Hotel</a><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: OpenSansRegular, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;\">&nbsp;is located in the Somerset village of Hatch Beauchamp, in a building dating back to the 18th century. The 11 rooms are individually styled with antique furniture befitting the setting, and come with en suite bathroom, Freeview television and views of the landscaped gardens. The hotel produces its own fruit, vegetables and meat where possible, and sources the rest from local farmers, to produce home-grown ingredients for use in the restaurant, which supplies guests with breakfast, lunch and dinner. The venue caters for weddings, corporate functions and private parties, with packages tailored to individual requirements.</span></p>','BS4 3EN','51.4426688','-2.5683698999999933',NULL,NULL,1,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'2014-07-28 00:00:01','2014-07-28 13:49:27','2014-07-28 01:50:27',0),
	(338,NULL,NULL,2,'Tea Tuesdays! at Caffe Clifton','tea-tuesdays-at-caffe-clifton',' Caffe Clifton has led to the introduction of a regular â€˜Tea Tuesdayâ€™','<p><span style=\"font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">The roaring success of tea tasting event at Caffe Clifton has led to the introduction of a regular &lsquo;Tea Tuesday&rsquo;.</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\" /><span style=\"font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">The last Tuesday of every month gives you an opportunity to see tea in a new light.</span></p>','<p><span style=\"font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">Anne the owner of Attic Tea introduces you to the tea drinking culture. The group tastes the teas along with the different blends Attic designs.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\" /><span style=\"font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">Following the event there is a chance for the new found tea lovers to purchase their favourite of the evening as well as the much acclaimed Attic Tea pots.&nbsp;</span></p>','BS4 3EN','51.4426688','-2.5683698999999933',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,'2014-07-29 00:00:01','2014-07-29 09:11:04','2014-07-29 09:12:31',0),
	(339,NULL,NULL,2,'Sunday Riverside Roast at Beeses with Bristol Ferry Boats','sunday-riverside-roast-at-beeses-with-bristol-ferry-boats','Take a scenic cruise to Beeses Bar & Tea Gardens.','<p><span style=\"font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">Head up through the Feeder Canal and along the leafy river banks of St Anne\'s, with ducks, swans and the occasional kingfisher to see on the way.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\" /><span style=\"font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">You will be amazed at the beauty and tranquility right on our doorstep. Past the boat house, nestled in this beautiful valley on the water\'s edge, are the lovely Gardens.</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\" /><span style=\"font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">On arrival, your table will be set and as your roast dinner is already ordered so there\'s no need to queue. This is a great way to spend sunday morning and lunchtime in an idyllic location.</span></p>','<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\">You can choose from ROAST BEEF with yorkshire pud and all the trimmings or ROAST PORK or VEGETABLE AND NUT ROAST.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />This is a freshly prepared and delicious roast made using fresh veg and locally sourced meat where possible.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\">Time: 11am - 2pm (3 hour river trip including Sunday roast at Beese\'s)<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />Prices: &pound;21 for adults and seniors &amp; &pound;15 for childrens meals (including the ferry fare).</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />Call the ferry office on 01179273416 to book seats or speak to the crew out on the ferries.</p>','BS4 3EN','51.4426688','-2.5683698999999933',NULL,NULL,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL,'2014-07-29 00:00:01','2014-07-29 09:14:19','2014-07-29 09:15:20',0),
	(340,NULL,NULL,2,'Market at the Moon','market-at-the-moon','The Market at the Moon is an event that emphasises local trade and talent','<p><span style=\"font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">The Market at the Moon is an event that emphasises local trade and talent, sustaining the ethically inclined community there is in Stokes Croft, Bristol. All events provide a place to find all kinds of small, independent trades, so you can effortlessly discover and enjoy the unique and loved goods your community can provide.</span></p>','<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\">Every week will have a range of stalls including:</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\">Vintage Collectors // Raw Chocolatiers // Jewellery Makers // Upcycled Clothing // Vinyl // Fresh Hot Chai // Xmas Cards &amp; Decor // Hand Embellished Tee\'s // Peruvian Wares // Artists // // Wooden Decor // Books // Cakes // Leather // Organic Treats // Miniature Frames // SamBra Scarves // Fascinators // RSPB Awareness // various musicians, workshops and fresh food!</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />Note: If the forecast is poor the market will be cancelled.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />Time: every saturday from 12pm to 6pm<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />Free</p>','BS4 3EN','51.4426688','-2.5683698999999933',NULL,NULL,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL,'2014-07-29 00:00:01','2014-07-29 09:15:23','2014-07-29 09:16:46',0),
	(341,NULL,NULL,2,'Bristol 2014','bristol_2014','World War I had a profound effect on Bristol and its people','<p><span style=\"color: #282828; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.719999313354492px;\">World War&nbsp;I had a profound effect on Bristol and its people, even though it was not a direct part of the \'theatre of war.\' The city played an important role in the war, as a hub of transport and industry. Individual lives and communities were changed forever.</span></p>','<p><span style=\"color: #282828; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.719999313354492px;\">2014 marks the 100-year anniversary of WW1. There is a collection of events across the city to commemorate the centenary in Bristol.</span></p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL,'2014-07-29 00:00:01','0000-00-00 00:00:00','2014-07-29 09:23:31',28),
	(342,NULL,NULL,2,'Watershed Cafe Bar','watershed_cafe_bar','Open All Year','<p><span style=\"font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">Open every day from early in the morning to late at night, we offer breakfast, lunch and evening meals, all following a simple policy: stay fresh, local and seasonal. Enjoy our food, get some drinks in with friends or relax with a coffee and use our free wi-fi &ndash; the choice is up to you.</span></p>','<p><span style=\"font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">Watershed has an ethical, sustainable approach to food. Our Plot to Plate policy literally means straight from the farmers plot in the ground and onto your dinner plate. A great result of this is that our food is really fresh and hasn&rsquo;t had to travel hundreds of miles to get here.</span></p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL,'2014-07-29 00:00:01','0000-00-00 00:00:00','2014-07-29 09:25:59',29),
	(343,NULL,NULL,2,'Hotel du Vin & Bistro','hotel_du_vin_bistro','Open All Year','<p><span style=\"font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">Hotel du Vin &amp; Bistro in central Bristol is open seven days a week for lunch and dinner, with the Bistro offering a menu rooted in classic European cuisine with a contemporary edge.</span></p>','<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\">Praised in the national press time and time again, tables at the Hotel du Vin &amp; Bistro are highly sought after. The Bistro menu changes daily, featuring classic dishes supporting a philosophy of quality food cooked simply with the freshest of local ingredients, and all sensibly priced.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\">Private dining and wine-tasting experiences available.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL,'2014-07-29 00:00:01','0000-00-00 00:00:00','2014-07-29 09:28:25',30);
